**Critical issue:** This code will **not work without proper Express middleware setup**. The webhook handler (line 21) requires custom middleware to capture `req.rawBody` before body parsing:

```typescript
app.use(express.json({
  verify: (req, res, buf) => {
    req.rawBody = buf.toString('utf8');
  }
}));
```

Without this, all webhooks will fail signature verification silently.
